snippet: With the help of a rise in home prices, the mortgage giant Fannie Mae posted quarterly earnings of $10.1 billion.
abstract: Fannie Mae reports second-quarter profit of $10.1 billion, up from $5.1 billion in same period year earlier; company, which is owned by government, has turned profit in each of past six quarters.
lead_paragraph: With the help of a rise in home prices, the mortgage giant Fannie Mae posted quarterly earnings of $10.1 billion.
